      "writtenOn": "2017-08-07T17:11:06Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I don\u0027t care too much, just wanted to point out that if most people use the short options most of the time, the long ones might actually be less intuitively-readable.  I do agree that in general, since we\u0027re not having to type these out every time, we can afford to be more verbose in scripts if it helps readability.\n\nSo... LGTM?",
